	   <tr><td colspan=2>Some tips for the soloing magicians:<br>Get pets as soon as you can. They are the key to success.<br><br>Be extremely careful when casting area of effect spells. They can easily pull more monsters into the fight than you wanted to.<br><br>Never forget you are a mage not a tank. Step back and cast if you get to half life.<br><br>Concentrate on raising your INT, AGI, AC, & Mana. You'll be thankful you did.<br><br>Majhik<br>Mage of the 10th Order<br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
