	   <tr><td colspan=2>I'm one-week old into the game so could someone please answer me the following questions: <br><br>(1) which of the true spellcaster classes is best (in the long run i.e. at higher levels) and most importantly, WHY? I cannot decide whether to make a necromancer, magician, or wizard. <br><br>(2) I've read that wizards can deal quick strike DD and such, but in a fair and equal (high level) fight, what would be the best? <br><br>(3) And how about the best class for soloing? <br><br>I assume that since this is the magician's forum, the answers will be mages (-:&nbsp;&nbsp;That's fine b/c I am leaning towards making a cute little, female, gnome magician anyways! <br><br>Thanks to all who answer (and read this msg)!<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
