	   <tr><td colspan=2>I never saw giant toes when I went to the merchant on AC isle.*shrug*. Also, the earth pet has the same HP with the focus item, just a lot more agility. Since the earth pet's natural agility is about 70, it normally gets hit a LOT more than usual and takes a lot of damage per hit. This is becuase if your agility is below 75 your chances of getting hit increase a LOT and your AC also takes a plunge. The focus item makes it so that your earth pet now has above 75 agility, which makes a HUGE difference.<br><br>The pets DID seem to hit a bit harder with the focus items, so the focus items probably grant a bonus to strength and/or atk.<br>&nbsp;<br></td></tr>
